subject: Re: Attention please
body:
Dear Mr. Wrey,

Thank you for your message. However, I must inform you that there seems to be a misunderstanding. I have not been involved in any transactions involving large sums of money or a box full of funds.

I would appreciate it if you could provide more details about this situation, as I am currently unable to assist without further information.

Best wishes,
Julie
